snippet.title: Wrath of the Lich King Classic Announce Cinematic Trailer | World of Warcraft
snippet.description:
Something stirs in the icy hills as a bone-numbing chill spreads throughout Northrend. Relive the legend once again with Wrath of the Lich King Classic – coming 2022. Learn more at http://wowclassic.com. #WrathClassic #Warcraft
